title: Replies to initial written questions raised by Finance Committee Members in examining the Estimates of Expenditure 2010-11
question_text: The Bureau will “co-ordinate the allocation of resources for minor building works” in 2010-11. What are the projects pending approval in 2010-11? How much money is involved in each of them? What were the projects approved in 2009-10? How much money was involved in each of them?
reply_text: The Treasury Branch co-ordinates the allocation of resources for minor building works funded under the block vote Head 703 Subhead 3101GX, in respect of which Director of Architectural Services is the Controlling Officer. Up to 9 March 2010, the Architectural Services Department has received applications for 12 minor building works projects (each costing over $1.4 million) which are pending approval in 2010-11, at a total estimated project cost of about $93.040 million. Please refer to Annex A for details. We expect more new projects will be submitted for funding approval during the course of 2010-11. In 2009-10 (up to 9 March 2010), 50 minor building works projects (each costing over $1.4 million) have been approved at a total project cost of $341.702 million. Please refer to Annex B for details. There are many minor building works projects each costing $1.4 million or less, which mainly cover minor alterations, additions and improvements initiated by bureaux/departments throughout the financial year to meet their operational needs and to cope with changes in public service requirements. In 2009-10 (up to 9 March 2010), about 3 100 such projects at a total project cost of about $314.31 million were approved. Up to 9 March 2010, applications for about 135 such projects have been received and are pending approval in 2010-11. As the majority of these improvement works are minor in nature, we have not set out the details of these projects in this reply. Signature Name in block letters STANLEY YING Permanent Secretary for Financial Post Title Services and the Treasury (Treasury) Date 16 March 2010 Annex A List of minor building works projects pending approval in 2010-11 (with a project estimate of over $1.4 million each) Annex B List of minor building works projects approved in 2009-10 (up to 9 March 2010) (with an approved project estimate of over $1.4 million each)
